My Motto

About Me   "Determination, Hard Work, Fun"

A workaholic guy with over 3+ years of professional experience & 6+ years personal freelancing experience in game & interactive application development. Loves to design & develop new and interactive games & applications for Augmented Reality, Virtual Reality, PC, Android, iOS, WebGL platforms, Oculus Rift etc. Experienced in working with server mechanics and backend data handling for Unity applications. Always interested in trying and learning new and interesting things. Currently getting experience in making Unity communications with Node.JS server, HTML, Javascript & .jslib, interactions with browser scripting. Looking forward to learn machine learning mechanics with Unity in near future. Gamer and game lover

Virtual Event Platform

(Immersive Social Experience)

[Professional Project]

Virtual Event Platform (VEP) is an industry agnostic solution, which allows event organizers and exhibitors to harness the power of VR and gamification to create interactive, online events that eliminate the need for common logistical and travel-related expenses. The VEP brings people together regardless of their location in a virtual multiplayer environment.

Role: Lead developer

Platforms: Android, iOS, Windows, Mac, WebGL, Mobile VR

(A product of AVIANET. All rights reserved by AVIANET)

Predictive Maintenance

(AR/VR Machine Maintenance Prediction)

[Professional Project]

Today, manufacturing and other industries are trying to improve their competitiveness by combining manufacturing and other business processes with information technology. Virtual & Augmented Realities are being used in training of technical workforce, machine maintenance, product development processes across enterprises as a helpful technology to achieve rapid consolidation of information and decision-making through visualization and experience. Harnessing the power of speech recognition, the user can perform checks just by voice commands.

Role: Lead Designer & Lead developer

Platforms: Android, iOS, Hololens

(A product of AVIANET. All rights reserved by AVIANET)

Product Showcasing AR

(AR Realtime Product Showcase)

[Customer Project]
Previous Next

What if you are able to check and place a product in your surrounding before purchasing it? The product showcasing AR app enables the user to select a product from a list of products available, fetched in realtime from backend database. And can place in their surrounding using surface/ground detection feature of AR. The producer has the ability to easily upload model and info of the product in the backend which can be fetched by consumers in realtime.

Role: Designer & developer

Platforms: Android

Tools Used:

  • Unity Game Engine
  • Blender

  • Adobe Photoshop
  • ARCore
  • MySQL
  • JSON
  • Unity Assetbundles

(AR Measurement)
